PS3 Dualshock Controller connected to Hobbytronics USB Host

This is an example Arduino Program to demonstrate reading the PS3 Controller data from the USB Host Board
See PS3 Controller product page (http://www.hobbytronics.co.uk/ps3-controller) and
USB Host product page (http://www.hobbytronics.co.uk/usb-host-board-v2)

Version 1.00	Initial Release